WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:08.800
Then preparing a modest gift should be fine

00:09.160 --> 00:10.160
Just to show our sincerity

00:11.400 --> 00:12.360
Modest gift

00:15.280 --> 00:16.120
Then later

00:16.160 --> 00:17.880
I'll have Xie Xuan go to the big restaurants

00:17.880 --> 00:18.880
And textile shops in the city

00:19.400 --> 00:20.400
Say he has

00:20.640 --> 00:21.040
Several pieces

00:21.040 --> 00:22.920
Of calligraphy and plaques with your inscriptions

00:23.160 --> 00:24.680
Let those who want them bid

00:24.920 --> 00:25.680
This

00:26.520 --> 00:28.000
Is really too embarrassing

00:28.640 --> 00:29.160
And

00:29.360 --> 00:30.400
How much money can this raise?

00:31.040 --> 00:31.920
Comparing wealth

00:32.000 --> 00:33.160
Our family can't match elder brother

00:33.680 --> 00:34.880
Since we can't compete in wealth

00:35.280 --> 00:36.400
Then we must compete in attitude

00:36.680 --> 00:37.760
Our Prince of Jin

00:37.760 --> 00:39.280
Is willing to even sacrifice his dignity

00:39.400 --> 00:40.760
For General Zu Kun

00:41.120 --> 00:42.040
This sincerity

00:42.280 --> 00:43.360
Is what truly matters

00:45.280 --> 00:46.360
My lady is right
